# Normalize line endings to LF on checkout across all platforms.
#
# GitHub's Windows runners default to core.autocrlf=true, which would
# otherwise check text files out as CRLF and trip the generated-file drift
# guards: xtask schema-check compares serde_yaml's LF output against
# schema/openapi.yaml, and the frontend codegen guard diffs generated.ts —
# both fail on a CRLF working tree. Every tracked file is LF today, so this
# enforces the status quo everywhere rather than rewriting any content.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never normalize or line-diff.
*.png   binary
*.ico   binary
*.icns  binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.webp  binary
*.ttf   binary
*.otf   binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.wasm  binary
*.pdf   binary
